Interface EventConverterI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractEventConverter, CompositeConverter, IdentityConverter

    public interface EventConverterI
extends java.io.Serializable
    The interface EventConverterI defines the method that must be implemented to convert events from a source type to a sink type.
